issue.title: Badges
issue.body: Added badge functionality to prometheus. Badges are stored in '/prometheus/badges/' and users have their own badges which track progress in '/prometheus/users/uid/data/badges/'. The badges can be accessed by using the getBadgeList() and getUserBadges() functions.
